<div class="card">
    <img src="https://media.gettyimages.com/id/1184184060/photo/cute-happy-dog-playing-with-a-stick.jpg?s=612x612&w=gi&k=20&c=13u3zhpxLm4OXoPn0roYfxnLer8iCrgJdWsXjImWCLg=" class="card-img-top" alt="">
